<PB REF="033741_0130_0FF8C204134A4F08">
<P>AMELIA; OR, THE FAITHLESS BRITON. AN ORIGINAL AMERICAN NOVEL, FOUNDED UPON RECENT FACTS. TO WHICH IS ADDED, AMELIA, OR MALEVOLENCE DEFEATED; AND, MISS SEWARD'S MONODY ON MAJOR ANDRE.</P>
<P>BOSTON: PRINTED FOR AND SOLD BY W. SPOTSWOOD, AND C. P. WAYNE. 1798.</P>
